{"word":"Τεμέση","slug":"Τεμέση","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n103050\" key=\"*teme/sh\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Τεμέση</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, a place whence (acc. to <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:1:184\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.184</biblScope> </bibl>) the Taphians obtained copper in exchange for iron: some identified it with Temesa in Bruttium; others read <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Ταμασόν</foreign> or <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Τάμασιν</foreign>, i.e. Tamassos in Cyprus, <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">v.</abbr> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0099.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:1:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Str.\">Str.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.1.5</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0525.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:6:8\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Paus.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.6.8</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ St.Byz.\">St.Byz.</a></author> </bibl>: <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὁ ἐν Τεμέσῃ ἥρως</foreign>, prov. of misplaced rage, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4083.tlg001:1409:14\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eust.\">Eust.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1409.14</biblScope></bibl>.</entryFree>"}]}